h1 {{pc.title}}
md-divider
.height-10
p Fill out the information below to start the payment process. You will get a chance to review before submitting. All payments must be submitted via Paypal.
div(layout, layout-sm='column', layout-wrap)
  md-input-container(flex='50')
    label First name
    input(data-ng-model='pc.data.firstName',required)
  md-input-container(flex='50')
    label Last name
    input(data-ng-model='pc.data.lastName',required)
  md-input-container(flex='100')
    label Entry name(s)
    input(data-ng-model='pc.data.brackets', required, name='brackets')
    div(ng-messages='paymentForm.brackets.$error')
      div(ng-message='required') List all of the brackets you are paying for. Separate them with commas. E.g. bracket1, bracket2
div(layout, layout-sm='column', layout-wrap).pad-top-15
  .height-10
  .text-muted.bold(flex='100') Number of Entries
  md-radio-group(data-ng-model='pc.data.numberOfEntries', flex='100')
    md-radio-button(value='1') One (1)
    md-radio-button(value='2') Two (2)
    md-radio-button(value='3') Three (3)
md-divider
.height-10
md-button(type='submit',ng-disabled='paymentForm.$invalid || !pc.data.numberOfEntries').md-raised.md-primary Start Payment Process
.height-10
i.fa.fa-2x.fa-cc-amex.pad-left-5
i.fa.fa-2x.fa-cc-mastercard.pad-left-5
i.fa.fa-2x.fa-cc-visa.pad-left-5
i.fa.fa-2x.fa-cc-discover.pad-left-5
.height-10
